backuppc (4.4.0-3) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Fix buffer overflow in `parse_input` when handling oversized frames.
  * Refactor `config_read` to support new options.
  * Fix regression introduced in 4.4.0-2 (Closes: #102030, #102031)
  * Also fixes (closes: #102032) with lowercase variant.
  * Fix Launchpad bug (LP: Bug #98765)
  * See discussion at https://bugs.debian.org/102030 for details.

 -- Axel Beckert <abe@debian.org>  Tue, 25 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0100

